    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Lighting devices that incorporate an array of LEDs within a bulb-shaped enclosure, usually made of glass. These are used for general lighting applications, in most cases as a replacement for incandescent light sources, as they offer more efficient energy performance.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
